# 🎨 UI Redesign — Aesthetic & Modern Sidebar + Dashboard

## Before vs After

````carousel
![Before — Dark, static, heavy sidebar](C:/Users/win 10/.gemini/antigravity/brain/6c7d7917-1e88-46a5-a308-3f85b408bdd6/before_ui.png)
<!-- slide -->
![After — Light, vibrant, animated sidebar](C:/Users/win 10/.gemini/antigravity/brain/6c7d7917-1e88-46a5-a308-3f85b408bdd6/after_ui.png)
